description: I have a 1448 jon boat that is very stable in the water ---- got a bigger one which made me 3 boats so no need for this one ---- it has a 25 hp 4-stroke Suzuki that has all new jets in the carbs ---- trailer has new tires/rims ---- bearings/seals and buddy bearings ---- new lights/wiring and new jack ---- less than 100 mi on trailer since this work was done ---- boat is in fair condition ----- could use a small weld in front where the winch hooks up and a small one at the back along the transom ---- other than that it wouldn't leak at all ---- it's an alumacraft riveted boat that has served me very well.  open to trades and all reasonable offers.
